          there had to be a better way.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Have you ever just wanted to find the best overall product in a genre, without wading
          through over-opinionated troll-spew?
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">Do you struggle finding good gifts for your significant (br)other?</p>
        <p class="mt-4">Look no further..</p>
        <p class="mt-4">Good stuff, for good bros.</p>
        <p class="mt-4">Welcome to <strong>Cool Toy, Bro! üòé</strong></p>
        <img alt="Cool Toy Bro Logo" class="block w-full h-auto" src="/cooltoybro_lg.png" />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-lg p-5 sm:mt-16 card">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold">How does it work?</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          For some links, we will recieve a small reward, should you decide to purchase a product.
          For others, we simply track whether or not you showed interest from us; nothing more. If
          you do decide to click one of the buy buttons on this site, seriously, bless up üôèüôå
