          I'm just a bro trying to break out of the matrix, and every one of your clicks gets me
          closer to that goal.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          In reward, we offer you this DJ Khaled random quote generator, which is actively
          maintained. Enjoy more life, more success, more blessings, more keys.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          You can <a href="/donate" class="underline">donate to the cause</a> if you feel compelled.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          For everything else, or you want a dope website like this one, email <span
            class="underline">mike@cooltoybro.com</span
          >
          and I'll get back to you as soon as I can.
        </p>
        <br />
        <Khaled />
